org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.scl.dtt.EnumTypeAdapter
All Implemented Interfaces:
IDataTemplate, IDTTComparable<TEnumType>
public class EnumTypeAdapter extends AbstractDataTypeAdapter<TEnumType>
A representation of the model object EnumType.

The following features are supported:

  1. Adapter
    • Returns the value of the DataTypeTemplateAdapter reference object
  2. Principal functions
    • Add TPrivate under this object
  3. Checklist functions
    • Compare Two TEnumType
    • Check whether TEnumType contain given value
